data.description: Spacious Sandpiper home on .33 acre awaits you.  Split floor plan home offers 4 bedrooms, 3 and a half bathrooms, 2 car garage, private pool, sizable flex room with fireplace, wet bar and bathroom.  Enjoy your cup of coffee by the pool, overlooking the peaceful views of the Saints Golf Course.  The owners suite offers full bathroom with double vanity, walk in closet, and sliding glass door to the pool.  Two HVAC systems allows you to easily control the temperatures in separate parts of the home.  The landscaping has been freshly updated with attention to detail.  The home is freshly painted and newer vinyl plank flooring in main living.  Turn this house into your home!
